translated: LEANDER, Sture Olof, Director, Captain, Hälsingborg, b. Stockholm 30/7 87, son of customs inspector Olof L and Hilda Junker, m. Angelika Schoug. Completed secondary school 07, reserve officer training 09, ship measurement competence 16. Assistant customs writer 07-21, head of the Land and Sea department of a mutual insurance company Hbgkont since 18, established assistant and agency company Sture Leander 19, representative for Thule Insurance Corporation, Skandinavien, Valkyrian, Jauthiod Shipping Insurance Corporation, AB Banankomp Stockholm since 20. Chairman and director of AB Sture L since 25, board member of Land & Sea since 29. Travel: Germany 21, 31, 34, 36, 37, France 31, 34, 37, Netherlands 31, 36, Belgium 31, 36, Italy 34. Freemason, member of Thule Insurance Corporation and Fylgias ftjM. Hobby: Advising people on organizing their finances by subscribing to protective insurances for themselves and their family.
